title: Committee selected to find senior vice provost for graduate, professional education (University of Delaware)
text: ( Source : University of Delaware ) 8:18 p.m., Oct. 1, 2015--A search committee has been appointed to find a senior vice provost for graduate and professional education, Charlie Riordan, deputy provost for research and scholarship, announced
